title: HealThy Self Co
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Raw, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has mostly vegan food and beverages, with the exception of honey, dairy and one sandwich with ham. Has a modern and inviting atmosphere. Take away smoothies, coffees, juices and teas are available. Order at counter. Also has an in-house naturopath and massage therapist.
